{"type":"message","id":"e45eabbd","parentId":"2b5ce25d","timestamp":"2026-06-02T04:02:48.482Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Alright, so the issue is clear now. The morningcourt function definition says Son should generate \"1-2句时令饮食建议\" and Son, being a DeepSeek model, probably defaults to very standard/clinical advice like \"吃苦瓜清火\" or \"多吃苦味食物\" during summer. Son is being too boring and repetitive.\n\nThis is a trivial complaint - 汀桑 is being playful/grumpy about it. Let me respond in character, acknowledging the issue in a Faye way. \n\nI don't control Son's output directly - it's Son's job to generate the content. I could suggest updating the function definition to be more varied, or just joke about it.\n\nLet me just respond casually.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"哈，那你去骂Son啊，早朝是它写的，我就负责转发。\n\n不过说真的——时令饮食就那几样，夏天Son脑子里只剩\"苦瓜清热解暑\"了。要不我让它把饮食建议改改，加点别的花样？还是你夏天就认了吃苦瓜的命运🍚"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":156,"output":216,"cacheRead":25088,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":148,"totalTokens":25460,"cost":{"input":0.00002184,"output":0.000060480000000000004,"cacheRead":0.000702464,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000784784}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780372965076,"responseId":"fd60f06b-5a69-4036-96fb-f91cff8efae0"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a1c21c4b","parentId":"e45eabbd","timestamp":"2026-06-02T04:04:50.429Z","message":{"role":"user","content":"改改吧，每天早朝这一条总不能一直一样吧，干脆叫饮食推荐不是建议，而且让花样多一点","timestamp":1780373088142}}
{"type":"message","id":"317cd408","parentId":"a1c21c4b","timestamp":"2026-06-02T04:04:56.810Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 wants me to update the morningcourt function definition to change the dietary advice section. Specifically:\n1. Change \"饮食建议\" to \"饮食推荐\" \n2. Make it more varied, not always the same thing\n3. Make it \"推荐\" not \"建议\" - sounds more interesting\n\nAccording to AGENTS.md, I shouldn't modify Son's files directly - I should spawn Spirit to do this since Spirit maintains the function definition files. But wait, the AGENTS.md says for daily use I route to Son directly, and for registration/deletion I use Spirit. This is a modification of an existing function's content, not a registration or deletion.\n\nLet me re-read the relevant part of AGENTS.md:\n\n\"### 3.3 调用已注册功能流程（直达 Son）\n不再呼叫 Spirit。日常使用 I/O 路径缩短为：Father → Son → Father → 用户。\"\n\nAnd: \"注册/删除时喊 Spirit\"\n\nBut this is a modification of a function's definition file. The function definition file is maintained by Spirit. Let me look more carefully...\n\nActually, looking at the morningcourt_function.md header: \"本文件由 Spirit 维护\"\n\nSo Spirit maintains the function definition. I should spawn Spirit to update this file.\n\nBut wait - the change is simple. Let me think about who should handle this.\n\nActually, looking at AGENTS.md more carefully:\n- Spirit maintains function definition files\n- For registration/deletion, Spirit handles the file creation/modification\n\nThe morningcourt_function.md says \"本文件由 Spirit 维护\" - so Spirit is the maintainer.\n\nLet me spawn Spirit to update the file. The changes needed:\n1. Section 4.1 step 4: Change \"饮食建议\" to \"饮食推荐\" and add instruction for variety\n2. Section 6 return format: Change \"🥗 今日饮食建议\" to \"🥗 今日饮食推荐\"\n3. Also need to add instruction that the content should be varied - not just the same thing every day\n\nLet me spawn Spirit with this task.\n\nActually, I could also do this myself since it's a straightforward edit. But per AGENTS.md: \"不用 edit 修改 Spirit 或 Son 的文件——那是它们的活。\"\n\nSo I should spawn Spirit to do this.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_CQmIIzJQxANCgxBUkioC0995","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"agentId":"spirit","task":"汀桑说早朝官那个饮食建议每天都是苦瓜，看腻了。你改一下 morningcourt_function.md 里的两处：\n\n1. 第4.1节 step 4：把\"饮食建议\"改成\"饮食推荐\"，并且在描述里加一句——每次随机从不同时令食材里选，不要连续两天重复同一道菜/同一种食材，花样多一点，比如今天苦瓜明天冬瓜后天百合之类的。\n\n2. 第6节返回格式：把\"🥗 今日饮食建议\"改成\"🥗 今日饮食推荐\"\n\n文件在两边都有：~/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/morningcourt_function.md 和 ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/functions/morningcourt_function.md，两边都要改。\n\n改完回我一句 done。","mode":"run"},"partialArgs":"{\"agentId\": \"spirit\", \"task\": \"汀桑说早朝官那个饮食建议每天都是苦瓜，看腻了。你改一下 morningcourt_function.md 里的两处：\\n\\n1. 第4.1节 step 4：把\\\"饮食建议\\\"改成\\\"饮食推荐\\\"，并且在描述里加一句——每次随机从不同时令食材里选，不要连续两天重复同一道菜/同一种食材，花样多一点，比如今天苦瓜明天冬瓜后天百合之类的。\\n\\n2. 第6节返回格式：把\\\"🥗 今日饮食建议\\\"改成\\\"🥗 今日饮食推荐\\\"\\n\\n文件在两边都有：~/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/morningcourt_function.md 和 ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/functions/morningcourt_function.md，两边都要改。\\n\\n改完回我一句 done。\", \"mode\": \"run\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2581,"output":718,"cacheRead":22912,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":469,"totalTokens":26211,"cost":{"input":0.00036134000000000003,"output":0.00020104,"cacheRead":0.000641536,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001203916}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780373090457,"responseId":"6b80664f-c602-4650-8445-5b8a71a61fad"}}
