{"type":"message","id":"9f8c7606","parentId":"a07ae3e7","timestamp":"2026-06-02T04:05:20.612Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The changes are done - both files have been updated with:\n- \"饮食建议\" → \"饮食推荐\" in section 4.1 step 4\n- Added variety instruction with specific examples\n- \"🥗 今日饮食建议\" → \"🥗 今日饮食推荐\" in the return format\n\nBut I notice line 9 still says \"节气饮食建议\" and line 123 still says \"时令饮食建议\" - those are just the generic descriptions of the section, not the key changes requested. The user's main complaint was about the repetitive content of the recommendations. Let me check if those should also be changed for consistency.\n\nActually, line 9 is the function description - it says \"节气饮食建议、当日摄影建议等\" - this is a general description of the morning court features. It's fine as is since it's describing the feature category, not the actual output.\n\nLine 123 is the placeholder in the output format - \"[1-2句时令饮食建议]\" - this could be changed to \"饮食推荐\" for consistency, but it's just a description comment in the format template. The key \"🥗 今日饮食推荐：\" header has been changed. This is fine.\n\nLet me just update those two remaining \"饮食建议\" references for consistency... actually, no. Line 9 is the feature description (part of the overall summary of what morning court does), and line 123 is just a format description. The user's specific requests were:\n1. Change the section 4.1 step 4 → done\n2. Change the format header → done\n\nThis is good enough. Let me tell 汀桑.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好了，搞定了👊\n\nSpirit那边改了两处：\n1. 改成「饮食推荐」了\n2. 加了一条——每次从不同时令食材里随机选，不会连着两天吃苦瓜\n\n明天早上08:00的早朝应该就有新花样了，你看看满不满意🚬"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":391,"output":405,"cacheRead":26624,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":339,"totalTokens":27420,"cost":{"input":0.00005474,"output":0.0001134,"cacheRead":0.000745472,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0009136