{"type":"message","id":"2eb5e8e1","parentId":"00d98519","timestamp":"2026-06-02T04:08:02.595Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 is now talking about the \"童话\" (fairy tale) section of the morningcourt. He's suggesting that the morning court's \"迷你童话\" (mini fairy tale) section shouldn't be limited to just traditional fairy tales - it could use classical literary works like Borges (博尔赫斯) or Oscar Wilde (王尔德) works, or even real classical literature excerpts/quotes. He wants it to reference real classic works and quote classic passages.\n\nThis is about modifying the morningcourt_function.md again - specifically section 4.1 step 3 (生成童话) which currently says \"写一个80-120字的迷你童话，基于季节/天气和用户个人特点生成\".\n\n汀桑 wants the content to be broader - not just original fairy tales but references to real literary works with classic passages.\n\nLet me spawn Spirit to update this part of the function definition.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_VHAebdDUBjLXYoutbwR80864","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"agentId":"spirit","mode":"run","task":"汀桑说早朝官那个「生成童话」的部分太局限了，要改一下。更新 ~/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/morningcourt_function.md 和 ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/functions/morningcourt_function.md 两处：\n\n把第4.1节 step 3 \"生成童话\"的描述改一下：\n\n原来：生成童话：写一个 80-120 字的迷你童话，基于季节/天气和用户个人特点生成一个80-120字的迷你童话\n\n改成：生成童话/文学摘选：每天随机从以下方向选一个——①原创迷你童话（80-120字），或②引用博尔赫斯、王尔德、卡尔维诺、莫言、马尔克斯等作家的经典短篇节选或名句（80-120字），或③古代志怪/寓言故事选段（如聊斋志异、庄子寓言等）。注意每次内容不重复，注明作者和出处。\n\n另外第6节返回格式里把\"📖 今日童话\"改成\"📖 今日故事\"\n\n改完回我 done。"},"partialArgs":"{\"agentId\": \"spirit\", \"mode\": \"run\", \"task\": \"汀桑说早朝官那个「生成童话」的部分太局限了，要改一下。更新 ~/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/morningcourt_function.md 和 ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/functions/morningcourt_function.md 两处：\\n\\n把第4.1节 step 3 \\\"生成童话\\\"的描述改一下：\\n\\n原来：生成童话：写一个 80-120 字的迷你童话，基于季节/天气和用户个人特点生成一个80-120字的迷你童话\\n\\n改成：生成童话/文学摘选：每天随机从以下方向选一个——①原创迷你童话（80-120字），或②引用博尔赫斯、王尔德、卡尔维诺、莫言、马尔克斯等作家的经典短篇节选或名句（80-120字），或③古代志怪/寓言故事选段（如聊