{"type":"message","id":"8ee235dc","parentId":"7c05fabc","timestamp":"2026-06-02T04:22:12.711Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is 汀桑, asking what I talked about with everyone yesterday (June 1st). This is a familiar user (8/10). Since this is a new session (different message_id and timestamp), let me check:\n\n1. It's June 2nd, 12:22 - this is a new session\n2. I need to read heart/dreams.md (recent dreams), heart/state.md (current state), and User.md to confirm who this is\n\nLet me load the necessary files. Since this is a new session (different day), I should do the full load:\n- Read User.md + impressions.md\n- Read encountings.md (recent 5)\n- Read heart/state.md\n- Read heart/dreams.md (recent 4)\n- Read heart/background.md\n\nActually, the User.md is already in context. Let me read the other files.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_VsZr1k41EmVSXeesLuqo5465","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204/encountings.md"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"/root/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204/encountings.md\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_01_DV2Kj7V53kLVcM4hr2hI5090","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-father/heart/dreams.md"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"/root/.openclaw/workspace-father/heart/dreams.md\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_02_gb0S62JpE8PpKGWwCgyS5312","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-father/heart/background.md"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"/root/.openclaw/workspace-father/heart/background.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":3078,"output":359,"cacheRead":27008,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":189,"totalTokens":30445,"cost":{"input":0.00043092000000000006,"output":0.00010052,"cacheRead":0.000756224,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001287664}},"stopReason":"toolU