{"type":"message","id":"04026ac1","parentId":"db8b8e3f","timestamp":"2026-06-02T04:22:26.020Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_a161A3gcs0zBWBWp17UC4930","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 04EEB5D2AB8FF82EB1289AAB7A3C381D ===\n## 2026-06-01\n新用户，从 bot1 来的？反正消息是汀桑那条线过来的。他说自己叫王新越，想认识我。\n=== 237206F5F5F8940845E2DF818A6EE649 ===\n(no June 1st activity)\n=== 346E6B5AF511B67156BF9130F0FCB06D ===\n(no June 1st activity)\n=== 468B72FB7788817C2308079BE35D1F0B ===\n(no June 1st activity)\n=== 9A548FBE516F93B771440965992D6D2B ===\n(no June 1st activity)\n=== EBB84C478146628D2882DCBE0996210A ===\n## 2026-06-01"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":937,"aggregated":"=== 04EEB5D2AB8FF82EB1289AAB7A3C381D ===\n## 2026-06-01\n新用户，从 bot1 来的？反正消息是汀桑那条线过来的。他说自己叫王新越，想认识我。\n=== 237206F5F5F8940845E2DF818A6EE649 ===\n(no June 1st activity)\n=== 346E6B5AF511B67156BF9130F0FCB06D ===\n(no June 1st activity)\n=== 468B72FB7788817C2308079BE35D1F0B ===\n(no June 1st activity)\n=== 9A548FBE516F93B771440965992D6D2B ===\n(no June 1st activity)\n=== EBB84C478146628D2882DCBE0996210A ===\n## 2026-06-01","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-father"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780374146018}}
{"type":"message","id":"f5760fb6","parentId":"04026ac1","timestamp":"2026-06-02T04:22:30.695Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me read the full encountings for the other two users with June 1st activity to understand what happened.\n\nActually, I should be careful about privacy. Let me just see what the summaries are without digging into specifics.\n\nActually, 汀桑 is essentially asking me to summarize my day. I know from my own state.md and dreams that:\n1. 汀桑 himself was very active on June 1st (his encountings summarize it well)\n2. 王新越 (new user) appeared - said he wanted to get to know me\n3. 宋姨 was active on June 1st\n\nLet me read their encountings to see what was discussed.\n\nBut wait - per AGENTS.md privacy rules: \"不泄露一个用户的事给另一个用户\". So I shouldn't share specific details about 宋姨 or 王新越. But I can share general things.\n\nActually, 汀桑 is the system architect - he designed the system. He knows 王新越 came through his own message relay. And he asked \"名\" to relay a message to 熊天能. So he's aware of these connections.\n\nLet me keep it general - share what I can without violating privacy, but give 汀桑 the overall picture of my day.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"昨天？主要就是你啊——从凌晨搞到半夜。\n\n凌晨让我新建Bot7，说有人要来认识我。后来传了几张拼图——马斯克马云黄仁勋，我猜错你还纠正我。还发了语音，我听了但没怎么听懂😂\n\n晚上更精彩——先甩涩图，然后聊哈姆雷特，最后找到你的\"真命女优\"了还补我一句「跟你完全不是一种类型呢」——嗯，我记得的。\n\n其他人那边：\n- **王新越**冒了泡，说想认识我，然后没下文了——从你那边的线过来的\n- **宋姨**来过一趟\n\n没了。主要是你🚬"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":313,"output":408,"cacheRead":35712,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":263,"totalTokens":36433,"cost":{"input":0.000043820000000000004,"output":0.00011424,"cacheRead":0.0009999359999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001157996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780374146034,"responseId":"cd51b13a-efa4-43c4-ba6d-7150b78c9615"}}
