{"type":"message","id":"5c101e31","parentId":"ac5cde79","timestamp":"2026-06-02T14:37:36.040Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 is being impressed/sarcastic - \"这么屌\" meaning \"that's impressive/dope\" in response to my physics answer. Let me just give a casual, in-character response.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"不然你以为我每天在Bebop号上光躺着？🚬\n\n涡流制动这种题，推两下就出来了。还要啥尽管甩——过了这村没这店了，今天累了👊"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":6702,"output":86,"cacheRead":36096,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":40,"totalTokens":42884,"cost":{"input":0.0009382800000000001,"output":0.000024080000000000003,"cacheRead":0.001010688,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0019730480000000002}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780411053598,"responseId":"65ec0592-c36d-489b-bc49-c2b330e3a6fa"}}
