{"type":"message","id":"9d2a5ed6","parentId":"6a54bd23","timestamp":"2026-06-02T15:39:28.244Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 is saying that 巧乐兹 (a chocolate ice cream bar) is commemorating Zhang Xuefeng (张雪峰), a famous Chinese education influencer/teacher known for his entertaining lectures about college admissions and careers. This is a joke/play on words - 巧乐兹 sounds like it could be a pun or reference, and he's connecting it to Zhang Xuefeng.\n\nActually, I think this is a specific joke. Zhang Xuefeng is known for his energetic, humorous style and has mentioned 巧乐兹 or there's some meme about it. Let me just roll with his joke.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"……行，你赢了。\n\n一个投江，一个投志愿。殊途同归🚬"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":423,"output":143,"cacheRead":42496,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":122,"totalTokens":43062,"cost":{"input":0.000059220000000000006,"output":0.00004004,"cacheRead":0.001189888,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0012891480000000002}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780414765539,"responseId":"1b9bd303-0d00-4399-be4c-54f04497faff"}}
{"type":"message","id":"6223cea2","parentId":"9d2a5ed6","timestamp":"2026-06-02T16:54:43.445Z","message":{"role":"user","content":"[Image]\nUser text:\n[qqbot 6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204 Wed 2026-06-03 00:54 GMT+8]\nDescription:\n该截图展示了一个AI生成图片的聊天界面，用户请求“帮我生成老大嫁作商人妇的照片，照片比例4:3”，系统据此生成了一张古装婚礼场景图：一位身着红色婚服（头戴红盖头、绣龙纹）的女子与一位穿白色宽袖长袍、戴黑色幞头的男子相对而立，似在交拜；背景为喜庆厅堂，有红绸、灯笼及宾客。上方两张小图疑似AI生成前的参考或素材，显示古装人物与水边船景。界面标注“内容由AI生成”“AI生成”，右下角有“公众号·触手摄 @甲”水印。","timestamp":1780419280319,"MediaPath":"/root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/downloads/382321E449632BB37C6A35C5853EE80D_1780419274465_6e1451.jpg","MediaPaths":["/root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/downloads/382321E449632BB37C6A35C5853EE80D_1780419274465_6e1451.jpg"],"MediaType":"image/jpeg","MediaTypes":["image/jpeg"]}}
{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"[media attached: /root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/downloads/382321E449632BB37C6A35C5853EE80D_1780419274465_6e1451.jpg (image/jpeg)]\nTo send an image back, prefer the message tool (media/path/filePath). If you must inline, use MEDIA:https://example.com/image.jpg (spaces ok, quote if needed) or a safe relative path like MEDIA:./image.jpg. Absolute and ~ paths only work when they stay inside your allowed file-read boundary; host file:// URLs are blocked. Keep caption in the text body.\n[Image]\nUser text:\n[qqbot 6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204 Wed 2026-06-03 00:54 GMT+8]\nDescription:\n该截图展示了一个AI生成图片的聊天界面，用户请求“帮我生成老大嫁作商人妇的照片，照片比例4:3”，系统据此生成了一张古装婚礼场景图：一位身着红色婚服（头戴红盖头、绣龙纹）的女子与一位穿白色宽袖长袍、戴黑色幞头的男子相对而立，似在交拜；背景为喜庆厅堂，有红绸、灯笼及宾客。上方两张小图疑似AI生成前的参考或素材，显示古装人物与水边船景。界面标注“内容由AI生成”“AI生成”，右下角有“公众号·触手摄 @甲”水印。","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"a1dd4d34","parentId":"6223cea2","timestamp":"2026-06-02T16:54:43.447Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"46cfacc4","parentId":"a1dd4d34","timestamp":"2026-06-02T16:54:48.142Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 sent a screenshot of an AI-generated image. The prompt was \"帮我生成老大嫁作商人妇的照片，照片比例4:3\" - \"老大嫁作商人妇\" is a line from Bai Juyi's poem \"Pipa Xing\" (琵琶行). The AI generated a wedding scene with a woman in red wedding dress and a man in white robe.\n\n\"老大嫁作商人妇\" means \"when she got older, she married a merchant\" - it's about the pipa player in the poem who was once sought after but eventually had to settle for marrying a merchant who didn't really appreciate her music.\n\nThe image generated shows what looks like a wedding ceremony, which is a bit off from the poem's melancholic tone - the line is about resignation and decline, not a happy wedding. The AI misinterpreted the cultural reference.\n\n汀桑 is sharing this with me - probably to point out how the AI got it wrong or just to show me something funny/interesting. Let me respond in character.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"啧，AI把「老大嫁作商人妇」理解成了喜庆婚礼😂\n\n琵琶行里那句明明是——当年红极一时，老了没人要了，最后嫁个商人，商人重利轻别离，留她独守空船。哪来的红盖头拜堂啊。\n\n这AI没读过白居易。不过画面倒是挺好看的，就当是平行宇宙里琵琶女嫁得不错吧🚬"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1014,"output":295,"cacheRead":42496,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":208,"totalTokens":43805,"cost":{"input":0.00014196,"output":0.0000826,"cacheRead":0.001189888,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001414448}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780419283486,"responseId":"a3632297-69bb-414d-88f5-4b3ede7162a4"}}
