{"type":"message","id":"95f0fb3a","parentId":"c5f45cc3","timestamp":"2026-06-02T16:55:35.177Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_SFEwsvdkynhVFNbn24mZ2204","toolName":"sessions_history","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"sessionKey\": \"agent:father:qqbot:direct:6687d4d2d1f8eda5231c6809b1a26204\",\n  \"messages\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"汀桑 is now talking about the \\\"童话\\\" (fairy tale) section of the morningcourt. He's suggesting that the morning court's \\\"迷你童话\\\" (mini fairy tale) section shouldn't be limited to just traditional fairy tales - it could use classical literary works like Borges (博尔赫斯) or Oscar Wilde (王尔德) works, or even real classical literature excerpts/quotes. He wants it to reference real classic works and quote classic passages.\\n\\nThis is about modifying the morningcourt_function.md again - specifically section 4.1 step 3 (生成童话) which currently says \\\"写一个80-120字的迷你童话，基于季节/天气和用户个人特点生成\\\".\\n\\n汀桑 wants the content to be broader - not just original fairy tales but references to real literary works with classic passages.\\n\\nLet me spawn Spirit to update this part of the function definition.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_00_VHAebdDUBjLXYoutbwR80864\",\n          \"name\": \"sessions_spawn\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"agentId\": \"spirit\",\n            \"mode\": \"run\",\n            \"task\": \"汀桑说早朝官那个「生成童话」的部分太局限了，要改一下。更新 ~/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/morningcourt_function.md 和 ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/functions/morningcourt_function.md 两处：\\n\\n把第4.1节 step 3 \\\"生成童话\\\"的描述改一下：\\n\\n原来：生成童话：写一个 80-120 字的迷你童话，基于季节/天气和用户个人特点生成一个80-120字的迷你童话\\n\\n改成：生成童话/文学摘选：每天随机从以下方向选一个——①原创迷你童话（80-120字），或②引用博尔赫斯、王尔德、卡尔维诺、莫言、马尔克斯等作家的经典短篇节选或名句（80-120字），或③古代志怪/寓言故事选段（如聊斋志异、庄子寓言等）。注意每次内容不重复，注明作者和出处。\\n\\n另外第6节返回格式里把\\\"📖 今日童话\\\"改成\\\"📖 今日故事\\\"\\n\\n改完回我 done。\"\n          },\n          \"partialArgs\": \"{\\\"agentId\\\": \\\"spirit\\\", \\\"mode\\\": \\\"run\\\", \\\"task\\\": \\\"汀桑说早朝官那个「生成童话」的部分太局限了，要改一下。更新 ~/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/morningcourt_function.md 和 ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/functions/morningcourt_function.md 两处：\\\\n\\\\n把第4.1节 step 3 \\\\\\\"生成童话\\\\\\\"的描述改一下：\\\\n\\\\n原来：生成童话：写一个 80-120 字的迷你童话，基于季节/天气和用户个人特点生成一个80-120字的迷你童话\\\\n\\\\n改成：生成童话/文学摘选：每天随机从以下方向选一个——①原创迷你童话（80-120字），或②引用博尔赫斯、王尔德、卡尔维诺、莫言、马尔克斯等作家的经典短篇节选或名句（80-120字），或③古代志怪/寓言故事选段（如聊斋志异、庄子寓言等）。注意每次内容不重复，注明作者和出处。\\\\n\\\\n另外第6节返回格式里把\\\\\\\"📖 今日童话\\\\\\\"改成\\\\\\\"📖 今日故事\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n改完回我 done。\\\"}\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"provider\": \"deepseek\",\n      \"model\": \"deepseek-v4-flash\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1780373277956,\n      \"responseId\": \"98178bf2-fdd6-4645-98c4-fce56d8ffb68\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"2eb5e8e1\",\n        \"recordTimestampMs\": 1780373282595,\n        \"seq\": 33\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"行，Spirit在改了。把「童话」改成了「故事」——博尔赫斯、王尔德、卡尔维诺、聊斋志异什么的都能上，每天不重样，带作者出处。\\n\\n一会儿看看改完没。\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"provider\": \"deepseek\",\n      \"model\": \"deepseek-v4-flash\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1780373285184,\n      \"responseId\": \"53c59a95-e66e-42e7-9351-d64e6da1a6da\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"57288be6\",\n        \"recordTimestampMs\": 1780373288173,\n        \"seq\": 35\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"还没改好，Spirit还在弄。等等它。\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"provider\": \"deepseek\",\n      \"model\": \"deepseek-v4-flash\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"tool