 \"fa8f1059\",\n        \"recordTimestampMs\": 1780373304825,\n        \"seq\": 40\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"Both files are updated correctly:\\n1. \\\"生成童话\\\" → \\\"生成童话/文学摘选\\\" with expanded content options\\n2. \\\"📖 今日童话\\\" → \\\"📖 今日故事\\\"\\n\\nBoth Spirit and Son are synced. Let me tell 汀桑.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"改好了👊\\n\\n早朝官两个地方都更新了：\\n\\n| 改什么 | 原来 | 现在 |\\n|--------|------|------|\\n| 标题 | 📖 今日童话 | 📖 今日故事 |\\n| 内容 | 只能原创童话 | 原创童话 / 博尔赫斯王尔德等经典摘选 / 聊斋庄子等古代寓言，三选一，带作者出处 |\\n\\n明天08:00的早朝就有新花样了——饮食不重样，故事也不只童话了。等着收吧🚬\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"provider\": \"deepseek\",\n      \"model\": \"deepseek-v4-flash\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1780373305005,\n      \"responseId\": \"a5b5a345-73a1-4e3b-bfa6-39cd02927aac\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"59e28b5c\",\n        \"recordTimestampMs\": 1780373307169,\n        \"seq\": 43\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": \"昨天你和大家聊了啥\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1780374127860,\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"7c05fabc\",\n        \"recordTimestampMs\": 1780374129444,\n        \"seq\": 44\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"The user is 汀桑, asking what I talked about with everyone yesterday (June 1st). This is a familiar user (8/10). Since this is a new session (different message_id and timestamp), let me check:\\n\\n1. It's June 2nd, 12:22 - this is a new session\\n2. I need to read heart/dreams.md (recent dreams), heart/state.md (current state), and User.md to confirm who this is\\n\\nLet me load the necessary files. Since this is a new session (different day), I should do the full load:\\n- Read User.md + impressions.md\\n- Read encountings.md (recent 5)\\n- Read heart/state.md\\n- Read heart/dreams.md (recent 4)\\n- Read heart/background.md\\n\\nActually, the User.md is already in context. Let me read the other files.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_00_VsZr1k41EmVSXeesLuqo5465\",\n          \"name\": \"read\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"path\": \"/root/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204/encountings.md\"\n          },\n          \"partialArgs\": \"{\\\"path\\\": \\\"/root/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204/encountings.md\\\"}\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_01_DV2Kj7V53kLVcM4hr2hI5090\",\n          \"name\": \"read\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"path\": \"/root/.openclaw/workspace-father/heart/dreams.md\"\n          },\n          \"partialArgs\": \"{\\\"path\\\": \\\"/root/.openclaw/workspace-father/heart/dreams.md\\\"}\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_02_gb0S62JpE8PpKGWwCgyS5312\",\n          \"name\": \"read\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"path\": \"/root/.openclaw/workspace-father/heart/background.md\"\n          },\n          \"partialArgs\": \"{\\\"path\\\": \\\"/root/.openclaw/workspace-father/heart/background.md\\\"}\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"provider\": \"deepseek\",\n      \"model\": \"deepseek-v4-flash\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1780374129472,\n      \"responseId\": \"084afdf6-c132-4c27-a9ce-12090719cd2a\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"8ee235dc\",\n        \"recordTimestampMs\": 1780374132711,\n        \"seq\": 45\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"汀桑 is asking about yesterday (June 1st) - what I talked about with everyone. This is a general question about my interactions with other users. I need to balance Faye's character - she's not going to just dump all conversations, especially since there's the privacy principle \\\"不泄露一个用户的事给另一个用户\\\". But 汀桑 knows the system, he knows there are other users, and he's asking about my overall day.\\n\\nLet me think about what I can share without violating privacy:\\n\\nFrom the encountings.md for 汀桑 himself on June 1st, I know what he did:\\n- Built Bot7\\n- Sent voice messages and puzzle pictures\\n- Talked about Musk, Ma, Huang\\n- Sent anime pics\\n- Talked about Hamlet\\n- Talked about his \\\"真命女优\\\" discovery\\n- Said \\\"跟你完全不是一种类型呢\\\"\\n\\nAs for other users on June 1st... I should check what other users were active. But per my rules, I can't \\\"泄露一个用户的事给另一个用户\\\". However, 汀桑 is asking about my day in general - he's essentially asking \\\"what happened with everyone yesterday\\\".\\n\\nLet me check who was active on June 1st among other users.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_00_4lLOj5HXmEcDBXaJXvEk0384\",\n          \"name\": \"exec\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"command\": \"ls ~/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/\"\n          },\n          \"partialArgs\": \"{\\\"command\\\": \\\"ls ~/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/\\\"}\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"provider\": \"deepseek\",\n      \"model\": \"deepseek-v4-flash\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1780374135385,\n      \"responseId\": \"2b2db200-43fd-4268-88d3-c6f2afc3b6a6\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"4fa25bef\",\n        \"recordTimestampMs\": 1780374138853,\n        \"seq\": 49\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"Let me check the encountings for other users that had activity on June 1st. But I need to be careful about privacy. Let me check which users had June 1st activity in their encountings.\\n\\nActually, let me think about this differently. 汀桑 is a system architect who helped build this system. He's not asking \\\"what did others say to you\\\" - he's asking \\\"what happened yesterday\\\". I can give him a general overview of my day without violating individual user privacy. \\n\\nBut I also need to be careful - AGENTS.md says \\\"不泄露一个用户的事给另一个用户\\\". So I shouldn't share specific conversations of other users.\\n\\nLet me describe my day in terms of general events, group by type, without naming specific users where it would be too private. Or I could just say \\\"mostly you\\\" since 汀桑 was the main one talking to me on June 1st.\\n\\nLet me check encountings for other users to see if there was June 1st activity.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_00_a161A3gcs0zBWBWp17UC4930\",\n          \"name\": \"exec\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"command\": \"for d in ~/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/*/; do id=$(basename \\\"$d\\\"); if [ \\\"$id\\\" != \\\"README.md\\\" ] && [ \\\"$id\\\" != \\\"_template\\\" ] && [ \\\"$id\\\" != \\\"6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\\\" ]; then echo \\\"=== $id ===\\\"; grep -A1 \\\"^## 2026-06-01\\\" \\\"$d/encountings.md\\\" 2>/dev/null || echo \\\"(no June 1st activity)\\\"; fi; done\"\n          },\n          \"partialArgs\": \"{\\\"command\\\": \\\"for d in ~/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/*/; do id=$(basename \\\\\\\"$d\\\\\\\"); if [ \\\\\\\"$id\\\\\\\" != \\\\\\\"README.md\\\\\\\" ] && [ \\\\\\\"$id\\\\\\\" != \\\\\\\"_template\\\\\\\" ] && [ \\\\\\\"$id\\\\\\\" != \\\\\\\"6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\\\\\\\" ]; then echo \\\\\\\"=== $id ===\\\\\\\"; grep -A1 \\\\\\\"^## 2026-06-01\\\\\\\" \\\\\\\"$d/encountings.md\\\\\\\" 2>/dev/null || echo \\\\\\\"(no June 1st activity)\\\\\\\"; fi; done\\\"}\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"