spond in Faye's character - short, a bit lazy (it's late), but with a fun take.\\n\\nThe question is basically: ancient people ate zongzi (for Dragon Boat Festival/qu yuanzi/commemoration of Qu Yuan, also seasonal) and modern people eat 巧乐兹 ice cream - same reason? \\n\\nI think he's making a playful connection between 粽子 and 巧乐兹 - both wrapped in something (bamboo leaves vs chocolate/waffle cone), both associated with summer/heat, etc. Or maybe he's asking if it's both about cooling down/comfort food.\\n\\nActually, 巧乐兹 is a brand of ice cream bar (chocolate-coated ice cream). The comparison to zongzi - both are wrapped, both are eaten in summer. But the cultural significance is different - zongzi for Dragon Boat Festival commemorating Qu Yuan, 巧乐兹 is just modern ice cream.\\n\\nLet me give a short, fun Faye-style answer.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"哈？🤔\\n\\n粽子纪念屈原，巧乐兹纪念——你馋了。\\n\\n不过要说像的话……都是裹着东西吃、都是夏天的仪式感。一个是要投江喂鱼，一个是要投进你嘴里。\\n\\n就这区别🚬\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"provider\": \"deepseek\",\n      \"model\": \"deepseek-v4-flash\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1780414706614,\n      \"responseId\": \"8891045e-c2da-4fdb-ac39-dafc5842f4d5\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"0df6df98\",\n        \"recordTimestampMs\": 1780414712286,\n        \"seq\": 66\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": \"巧乐兹纪念张雪峰\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1780414764074,\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"6a54bd23\",\n        \"recordTimestampMs\": 1780414765500,\n        \"seq\": 67\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"汀桑 is saying that 巧乐兹 (a chocolate ice cream bar) is commemorating Zhang Xuefeng (张雪峰), a famous Chinese education influencer/teacher known for his entertaining lectures about college admissions and careers. This is a joke/play on words - 巧乐兹 sounds like it could be a pun or reference, and he's connecting it to Zhang Xuefeng.\\n\\nActually, I think this is a specific joke. Zhang Xuefeng is known for his energetic, humorous style and has mentioned 巧乐兹 or there's some meme about it. Let me just roll with his joke.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"……行，你赢了。\\n\\n一个投江，一个投志愿。殊途同归🚬\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"provider\": \"deepseek\",\n      \"model\": \"deepseek-v4-flash\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1780414765539,\n      \"responseId\": \"1b9bd303-0d00-4399-be4c-54f04497faff\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"9d2a5ed6\",\n        \"recordTimestampMs\": 1780414768244,\n        \"seq\": 68\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": \"[Image]\\nUser text:\\n[qqbot 6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204 Wed 2026-06-03 00:54 GMT+8]\\nDescription:\\n该截图展示了一个AI生成图片的聊天界面，用户请求“帮我生成老大嫁作商人妇的照片，照片比例4:3”，系统据此生成了一张古装婚礼场景图：一位身着红色婚服（头戴红盖头、绣龙纹）的女子与一位穿白色宽袖长袍、戴黑色幞头的男子相对而立，似在交拜；背景为喜庆厅堂，有红绸、灯笼及宾客。上方两张小图疑似AI生成前的参考或素材，显示古装人物与水边船景。界面标注“内容由AI生成”“AI生成”，右下角有“公众号·触手摄 @甲”水印。\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1780419280319,\n      \"MediaPath\": \"/root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/downloads/382321E449632BB37C6A35C5853EE80D_1780419274465_6e1451.jpg\",\n      \"MediaPaths\": [\n        \"/root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/downloads/382321E449632BB37C6A35C5853EE80D_1780419274465_6e1451.jpg\"\n      ],\n      \"MediaType\": \"image/jpeg\",\n      \"MediaTypes\": [\n        \"image/jpeg\"\n      ],\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"6223cea2\",\n        \"recordTimestampMs\": 1780419283445,\n        \"seq\": 69\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"汀桑 sent a screenshot of an AI-generated image. The prompt was \\\"帮我生成老大嫁作商人妇的照片，照片比例4:3\\\" - \\\"老大嫁作商人妇\\\" is a line from Bai Juyi's poem \\\"Pipa Xing\\\" (琵琶行). The AI generated a wedding scene with a woman in red wedding dress and a man in white robe.\\n\\n\\\"老大嫁作商人妇\\\" means \\\"when she got older, she married a merchant\\\" - it's about the pipa player in the poem who was once sought after but eventually had to settle for marrying a merchant who didn't really appreciate her music.\\n\\nThe image generated shows what looks like a wedding ceremony, which is a bit off from the poem's melancholic tone - the line is about resignation and decline, not a happy wedding. The AI misinterpreted the cultural reference.\\n\\n汀桑 is sharing this with me - probably to point out how the AI got it wrong or just to show me something funny/interesting. Let me respond in character.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"啧，AI把「老大嫁作商人妇」理解成了喜庆婚礼😂\\n\\n琵琶行里那句明明是——当年红极一时，老了没人要了，最后嫁个商人，商人重利轻别离，留她独守空船。哪来的红盖头拜堂啊。\\n\\n这AI没读过白居易。不过画面倒是挺好看的，就当是平行宇宙里琵琶女嫁得不错吧🚬\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"provider\": \"deepseek\",\n      \"model\": \"deepseek-v4-flash\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1780419283486,\n      \"responseId\": \"a3632297-69bb-414d-88f5-4b3ede7162a4\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"46cfacc4\",\n        \"recordTimestampMs\": 1780419288142,\n        \"seq\": 70\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": \"分析笑点\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1780419288834,\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"42ef2d7d\",\n        \"recordTimestampMs\": 1780419290229,\n        \"seq\": 71\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"汀桑让我分析这个笑点。这其实是个AI生成图片的乌龙——Prompt是\\\"老大嫁作商人妇\\\"（琵琶行名句，讲的是年老色衰的琵琶女最后嫁给了商人，独守空船很凄凉），但AI理解成了婚礼场景，生成了喜庆的红盖头拜堂图。\\n\\n笑点在于：\\n1. 字面理解和文学理解的错位——AI只理解了\\\"嫁\\\"和\\\"商人\\\"这两个词，不知道\\\"老大\\\"在这里是\\\"年纪大了\\\"的意思，直接当成了喜庆婚礼\\n2. 琵琶行原诗的氛围是凄凉哀怨的，AI生成了红红火火的热闹场面\\n3. 文化梗——这是白居易的名篇，稍微有点文学常识都知道不是喜庆的事\\n\\n让我用Faye的风格给他分析。\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"笑点结构拆一下：\\n\\n**第一层：字面误会**\\nAI看到「老大嫁作商人妇」= 提取关键词「嫁」「商人」「妇」\\n→ 合理联想：婚礼、红盖头、拜堂\\n→ 生成了一幅喜庆婚宴图\\n\\n**第二层：文化断层**\\n原文语境：琵琶女年轻时红极一时 → 老了没人要 → 嫁商人 → 商人重利轻别离 → 独守空船\\n白居易写的是凄凉，AI理解成喜庆\\n这中间的落差有多大，笑点就有多大\\n\\n**第三层：反讽**\\n写这句诗的年代，女人嫁商人本身就是\\\"下嫁\\\"——士农工商，商人最低等\\n结果AI给整成了红绸灯笼高朋满座的热闹婚礼\\n等于说：AI不仅没读懂诗，连历史阶级也没搞懂\\n\\n**第四层：叠buff**\\n你特意写了「照片比例4:3」——连比例都对了，内容全歪\\n精准的格式 + 离谱的理解 = 完美反差\\n\\n总结：AI用最高清的画质、最认真的构图，画了一个最不可能发生的结局。就像给祥林嫂配了个happy ending的BGM😏\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"provider\": \"deepseek\",\n      \"model\": \"deepseek-v4-flash\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1780419290264,\n      \"responseId\": \"632df517-14ce-49b2-a7e6-85d4e7ac8d06\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"8260657a\",\n        \"recordTimestampMs\": 1780419296421,\n        \"seq\": 72\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": \"笑点是新娘是科比\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1780419309469,\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"aec16588\",\n        \"recordTimestampMs\": 1780419310818,\n        \"seq\": 73\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"汀桑 is saying the real punchline is that the bride is Kobe Bryant (科比). So the AI generated Kobe Bryant wearing a red wedding dress and veil as the \\\"bride\\\" in the Merchant's Wife scene.\\n\\nLet me look at the image again more carefully to see if I can spot Kobe in it.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_00_rKkyjmLIwbuRQIGY6iz11247\",\n          \"name\": \"image\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"image\": \"/root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/downloads/038E110974F0E51CAA061261D4347E0A_1780410607454_aaf5e5.jpg\",\n            \"promp